    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 1,
    "text": "、いいよ。",
    "start_time": 3302.64,
    "end_time": 3304.12,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "text": "そしてお、愛莉ちゃん。",
    "start_time": 3305.64,
    "end_time": 3307.66,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 3,
    "text": "特訓後でござい。",
    "start_time": 3307.66,
    "end_time": 3309.04,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 4,
    "text": "この、さっきの穂乃果ちゃんが着てた衣装と似てるよう、",
    "start_time": 3310.32,
    "end_time": 3315.1,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 5,
    "text": "ちょっとスカートの部分とかが、若干違うんだ、愛莉ちゃんはお花がねパニエみたいにバーって乗って、",
    "start_time": 3315.1,
    "end_time": 3322.0,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 6,
    "text": "すっごい可愛いよ。",
    "start_time": 3322.0,
    "end_time": 3323.6,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 7,
    "text": "なんか見ちゃう。",
    "start_time": 3327.2,
    "end_time": 3328.28,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 8,
    "text": "このの周りにちりばめられた雫、なんか雨が上がった後みたいな。",
    "start_time": 3329.8,
    "end_time": 3334.56,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 9,
    "text": "なんかこう感じもすっごいこのストーリーを彷彿とさせる。",
    "start_time": 3335.52,
    "end_time": 3340.44,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 10,
    "text": "そしてこちらは特訓。",
    "start_time": 3341.44,
    "end_time": 3343.02,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 11,
    "text": "これ、、、ストーリーの中でもあったけど愛莉ちゃんは本当、",
    "start_time": 3343.02,
    "end_time": 3349.1,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 12,
    "text": "いっつも心配して、雫のこと。",
    "start_time": 3349.1,
    "end_time": 3353.4,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 13,
    "text": "あんた?",
    "start_time": 3353.4,
    "end_time": 3354.28,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 14,
    "text": "って言ってくれるんだ。",
    "start_time": 3354.28,
    "end_time": 3355.72,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 15,
    "text": "雫はやっぱそういうの言わなかったりするから",
    "start_time": 3355.72,
    "end_time": 3358.24,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 16,
    "text": "。",
    "start_time": 3359.54,
    "end_time": 3360.04,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 17,
    "text": "常に心配してくれるんだよ。",
    "start_time": 3360.04,
    "end_time": 3362.08,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 18,
    "text": "本当、。",
    "start_time": 3363.28,
    "end_time": 3364.44,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 19,
    "text": "愛莉ちゃん愛莉ちゃんがいなかったら今の雫もないし。",
    "start_time": 3364.44,
    "end_time": 3368.72,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 20,
    "text": "、シアター時代も愛莉ちゃんのね9T時代の愛莉ちゃんにいっぱい励ましてもらったんで、",
    "start_time": 3369.56,
    "end_time": 3377.7,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 21,
    "text": "この2人の関係が見える。",
    "start_time": 3377.7,
    "end_time": 3380.48,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 22,
    "text": "そして遥。",
    "start_time": 3381.44,
    "end_time": 3382.56,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
